    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Anderson,",
        "I am John Cooper, and I have premium travel Insurance with your company. I am writing to claim insurance on my lost laptop.",
        "To begin with, I have lost my Dell i5 Core laptop, which was Red in colour. Just 6 months back I had purchased it, and it was worth 65000 INR. I still have the receipt with me if you need it.",
        "Furthermore, I lost it, when I was changing my flight from Pune to Mumbai. I boarded my flight in Delhi and via Pune I was flying to Mumbai.  While changing my flight in Pune, I lost my laptop. I stopped for a coffee and suddenly I heard the announcement for my flight, and request to board the flight as soon as possible. I forgot my laptop, where I sat for coffee.",
        "Nevertheless, mercifully, I have premium travel cover my lost items. I will really appreciate your efforts if you credit the money into my credit card or contact me for any other form of payment methods. Kindly find my business card for my contact details.",
        "Looking forward to hearing from you soon.",
        "Yours Faithfully,",
        "John Cooper."
